text: Bikmetovo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Tatar-Ulkanovsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 109 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 23 km from Tuymazy, 11 km from Tatar-Ulkanovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Bikmetovo
